    "While it drives innovation, it can be difficult for researchers and professionals to stay current.",
    "Smaller enterprises or resource-constrained institutions may struggle to maintain access to cutting-edge tools, resulting in a widening gap in innovation capabilities.",
    "This issue highlights the importance of creating accessible training programs, standardized development frameworks, and open-source AI platforms.",
    "These resources empower individuals and organizations of various scales to contribute to advancements in sensory science.",
    "Collaborative outreach programs and publicly funded resources can bridge gaps and democratize access to AI technologies."
